setup <- function() {
  createCanvas(400, 300)
}

draw <- function() {
  background(0, 0, 33) # RGB colors

  for (i in 1:3) {
    dia <- sin(frameCount * 0.025) * 30 * i
    fill(255, 70 * i, 0) # RGB colors
    circle(100 * i, 150, dia) # (x, y, diameter)
  }
}
